 		<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Funding woes could &#8216;cripple&#8217; NM spaceport as other states invest in space race</h1>
 		<h5 class="byline"><span class="by-author"><span class="by">By</span> <span class="author vcard" itemprop="author"><a class="url fn n" href="https://nmpolitics.net/index/author/heath-haussamen/" title="More from Heath Haussamen, NMPolitics.net" rel="author">Heath Haussamen, NMPolitics.net</a></span></span><span class="sep"> | </span><time class="entry-date updated dtstamp pubdate" datetime="2017-08-22T06:59:33-06:00">August 22, 2017</time></h5>

 		<div class="post-social clearfix"><div class="left"><span class="twitter"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="https://nmpolitics.net/index/2017/08/funding-woes-could-cripple-nm-spaceport-as-other-states-invest-in-space-race/" data-text="Funding woes could &#8216;cripple&#8217; NM spaceport as other states invest in space race" data-via="nmpoliticsnet" data-via="haussamen:Follow the author of this article" data-count="none">Tweet</a></span><span class="facebook"><fb:like href="https://nmpolitics.net/index/2017/08/funding-woes-could-cripple-nm-spaceport-as-other-states-invest-in-space-race/" send="false" layout="button_count" show_faces="false" action="like"></fb:like></span></div><div class="right"><span class="print"><a href="#" onclick="window.print()" title="Print this article" rel="nofollow"><i class="icon-print"></i> Print</a></span><span data-service="email" class="email custom-share-button icon-mail share-button"> Email</span></div></div>
